project structure

project_folder/
    |- app/
        |- __init__.py
        |- config.py contain db connection
        |- models.py table structure
        |- router.py api end points
        |- views.py  api logic
        |- main.py contain flask instance
        |- Dockerfile
        |- requirements.txt
    |- docker-compose.yml
    |- readme
    |- env python virtual environment
    |- .dockerignore
    |- .env environment variable
